{"tid":781241,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖少字]  西班牙法國漫遊","createTime":"2018-08-15T17:45:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T23:07:26.000Z","uid":11396,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0feab40325cb028dcf8fed18f33fcc9a4040d10a","tid":781241,"uid":11396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T17:45:24.000Z","msg":"是咁的 今年三月去左西班牙同巴黎兩星期 <br />\n主要想分享下少少相同埋路過見到既事<br />\n資料性既內容有需要可以再問 <br />\n<br />\n頭幾日係巴塞都係落狗屎 無咩圖直接skip啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去到馬德里終於見到成個trip第一次既陽光<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1796/44053146381_349be15bb2_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm2.staticflickr.com%2F1796%2F44053146381_349be15bb2_c.jpg&h=1fa23dc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1771/44004961442_7711475b64_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm2.staticflickr.com%2F1771%2F44004961442_7711475b64_c.jpg&h=7c023368&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1800/29116170617_6292386256_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm2.staticflickr.com%2F1800%2F29116170617_6292386256_c.jpg&h=6754938b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬德里王宮廣場<br />\n好多人係依度附近賣藝令氣氛好好 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1794/44053165471_7a8e22a5c8_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm2.staticflickr.com%2F1794%2F44053165471_7a8e22a5c8_c.jpg&h=cd7a0f6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1837/44053164651_8ce3787a5c_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm2.staticflickr.com%2F1837%2F44053164651_8ce3787a5c_c.jpg&h=8892a454&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1813/29116179897_ce6532e078_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm2.staticflickr.com%2F1813%2F29116179897_ce6532e078_c.jpg&h=fd8b1c80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1775/43147128195_feed5af67a_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm2.staticflickr.com%2F1775%2F43147128195_feed5af67a_c.jpg&h=d9e1d678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1796/42244071880_cdc0f72ace_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm2.staticflickr.com%2F1796%2F42244071880_cdc0f72ace_c.jpg&h=0d53220b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每次去旅行都會行下公園 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1792/29116226607_3d8edbc5c3_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm2.staticflickr.com%2F1792%2F29116226607_3d8edbc5c3_c.jpg&h=f34d0c7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1780/29116191277_800370a2d0_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm2.staticflickr.com%2F1780%2F29116191277_800370a2d0_c.jpg&h=c2e6e167&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多地攤既人幾個或者圍埋咁傾計過日晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1794/44004998432_5399430a3a_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm2.staticflickr.com%2F1794%2F44004998432_5399430a3a_c.jpg&h=d6968f44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1798/44004998372_732012d832_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm2.staticflickr.com%2F1798%2F44004998372_732012d832_c.jpg&h=c3ae0506&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依個鬼佬走左入去扮櫻花<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1835/42244065420_c5ccf425ae_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm2.staticflickr.com%2F1835%2F42244065420_c5ccf425ae_c.jpg&h=f3c96a3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影完就乖乖課金<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1834/43147062495_ab4d462d7e_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm2.staticflickr.com%2F1834%2F43147062495_ab4d462d7e_c.jpg&h=b5abac29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到個天窗好靚又影下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1792/42243962540_2f65d08462_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm2.staticflickr.com%2F1792%2F42243962540_2f65d08462_c.jpg&h=7ce865fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原本想去麗池公園 但係去到無開 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唯有影下圍欄出面既櫻花(?)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1797/29116182267_cdebfa4a17_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm2.staticflickr.com%2F1797%2F29116182267_cdebfa4a17_c.jpg&h=06a4925e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬德里就去到依度 中間都有去下教堂個D 不過就無咩影相<br />\n預告 下集會去托雷維耶哈 (粉紅色湖) <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8191310162d1e1bbb9100cd290f90a9382fb113b","tid":781241,"uid":93705,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T18:12:15.000Z","msg":"巴打用咩機影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n色好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abbc611930b25fec1ba8686d405b95771cd33b02","tid":781241,"uid":200142,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T19:23:34.000Z","msg":"個色調好靚啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a89d39be573a2d223f47922978678284bc1f7b","tid":781241,"uid":50196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T00:39:12.000Z","msg":"Spain 3月都會落雪？白雪雪好有冬日feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3284c2304b98e9ed010368e025052147cc31ba","tid":781241,"uid":16414,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T01:43:15.000Z","msg":"巴打係咪set 錯測光<br />\n好似over 咁嘅"},{"pid":"df05e9d9dfa03be45fcfacf387cd75669a95abe8","tid":781241,"uid":51200,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T05:27:46.000Z","msg":"我以為自己部手機個白平衡出左事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9750f16a8c4027afcc4457c61b3da43799dfbf1d","tid":781241,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T04:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44fd6037abb6ffff2707bb49029e97d0c0fc1b97","tid":781241,"uid":113141,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:28:41.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"4d6bfc82922a48212acb91e9ad5f9d93c1986927","tid":781241,"uid":72955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T23:07:26.000Z","msg":"馬德里自己去怕唔怕<br />\n好驚小偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}